                            <comment id="12924736" author="thejas" created="Mon, 25 Oct 2010 21:42:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch passes unit tests and test-patch .&lt;br/&gt;
The merging of schema for union-onschema has been moved to LOUnion.getSchema(). This way a schema is always available for the union-onschema during the parsing stage. The correct datatypes will be available in the schema returned by LOUnion.getSchema() after TypeChecking is complete.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
